# Project: Portfolio Website (Next.js)

## Tech Stack

- Next.js 16 (App Router), React 19, TypeScript 5
- Prisma 7 with Neon (serverless PostgreSQL via @neondatabase/serverless + @prisma/adapter-neon)
- TailwindCSS 4, Radix UI, shadcn, CVA + clsx + tailwind-merge
- AWS: Amplify, S3, SES, CloudFront (with presigner), Cognito
- Image processing: Sharp
- Auth: jose (JWT)
- Forms: react-hook-form + @hookform/resolvers + Zod 4
- State: Zustand, TanStack React Query
- Markdown: remark + rehype pipeline (remark-gfm, rehype-highlight, rehype-slug)
- Toast: Sonner
- Theming: next-themes

## Key Conventions

- API routes in src/app/api/
- Shared utilities in src/lib/
- Use Zod 4 for all validation
- Use withErrorHandler wrapper for all API routes
- Use ApiError class for error responses
- Auth middleware: requireAuth from src/lib/auth (jose JWT)
- All images converted to WebP via Sharp
- S3 keys follow pattern: {folder}/{entityId}/{variant}\_{fileId}.webp
- Use react-hook-form + @hookform/resolvers for all forms
- Use TanStack React Query for server state
- Use Zustand for client state
- Use Sonner for toast notifications
- UI components: Radix UI primitives via shadcn

## Commands

- Dev: npm run dev
- Build: npm run build
- Lint: npm run lint
- Type check: npx tsc --noEmit
- Test: npm test
- Type check: npx tsc --noEmit
- Prisma generate: npm run prisma:generate
- Prisma migrate: npm run prisma:migrate:dev
- Prisma studio: npm run prisma:studio

